{"tid":2315480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【Now新聞台】律師會強烈譴責恐嚇總裁判官蘇惠德的行為。","createTime":"2020-12-07T08:16:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T15:27:31.000Z","uid":25240,"like":2,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ffc49d99391256cf57e31b40fde83df7abc35c94","tid":2315480,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】律師會強烈譴責恐嚇總裁判官蘇惠德的行為。<br />\n<br />\n律師會發表聲明指，恐嚇司法人員是嚴重罪行，對法治及司法獨立造成無法容忍的威脅。法官及司法人員緊隨誓言要求，不偏不倚、無懼無偏履行職責，令公眾高度信任司法機構，任何人意圖藉恐嚇、對法官在裁決過程中施加壓力和影響，都不會動搖公眾對司法機構的信心。<br />\n<br />\n但必須制止恐嚇行為，保障司法人員、維護法治和司法獨立，呼籲執法機關將犯案者繩之於法。"},{"pid":"670cb97457e21e808ea86df704060528854c940a","tid":2315480,"uid":25240,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:17:09.000Z","msg":"何官被人淋紅油 = 睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201021/5GNSGEQXUBDIJBGAZDVCTK6F5E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201021%2F5GNSGEQXUBDIJBGAZDVCTK6F5E%2F&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYTlcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=7a1271c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201021%2F5GNSGEQXUBDIJBGAZDVCTK6F5E%2F&h=7a0fb737\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201021/5GNSGEQXUBDIJBGAZDVCTK6F5E/</a>"},{"pid":"89052b89595eb6e9100f793cab1f13bcffed2567","tid":2315480,"uid":44978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:17:13.000Z","msg":"邊個恐嚇佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13bc00ef25da35cf69acc4744bb1a4787a3a767","tid":2315480,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T08:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66645aa9200126e89db4d2496542d696b1c427c9","tid":2315480,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score